dct_title_s: Indiæ orientalis et insularum adiacentium antiqua et nova descriptio
dct_description_sm: Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margins.
Decorative cartouche with indigenous figure and fauna.
Shows topography, waterways, shoals, ports, routes.
